description:
Biden, the guy who was gonna fix covid, says "Winter of Death" is coming. Fauci (who makes Buck wish he could swear on the air) lies again. When will he lose credibility? YouTube dings us for sharing "medical misinformation" that is really just the widely reported opinions of two major airline CEOs -- who should know about the capabilities of their own planes. Heart-wrenching call from Kentucky tornado victim who calls out Biden for his time-wasting "photo-op." The left doesn't believe in free speech.
